{"tid":1146259,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦闖歐冠決賽 泰國男子兌現裸奔承諾","createTime":"2019-05-09T06:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T08:56:12.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"485f7895f1ecdf40c51c8261fd6b299aecb4c730","tid":1146259,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T06:51:10.000Z","msg":"利物浦闖歐冠決賽男子兌現裸奔承諾！<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;紅軍&rdquo;利物浦在歐冠盃半決賽郆馯妠中出現大逆轉，瘰栛以4比01打敗西甲豪門巴塞羅那，成為率先晉級決賽的隊伍，讓球迷欣喜若狂！<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;世界日報&rdquo;報導，泰諑果國橺漨一名男網友班雅曾許諾，若利物浦晉級，他就會裸奔！<br />\n<br />\n結果，利物浦果真獲勝，班雅也兌現承諾，繞著紅綠燈十字路口&ldquo;裸奔&rdquo;，引起網民高度關注。<br />\n<br />\n身材魁梧的班雅得知利物浦獲勝後，錄製視頻裸奔。從視頻中發現，他寫下利物浦4-0的戰績，跪下來拜了一下，便準備開始裸奔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://uf.cari.com.my/forumx/cforum/portal/201905/09/124019fb26fp7mpppfpid9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuf.cari.com.my%2Fforumx%2Fcforum%2Fportal%2F201905%2F09%2F124019fb26fp7mpppfpid9.png&h=f427bee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實他也不完全是裸奔，他把身上衣物脫剩一條橙色內褲，把屁股對向鏡頭，不停扭動屁股。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://uf.cari.com.my/forumx/cforum/portal/201905/09/124107u7l7126hr7l6jpdh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuf.cari.com.my%2Fforumx%2Fcforum%2Fportal%2F201905%2F09%2F124107u7l7126hr7l6jpdh.png&h=4403922c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一切準備就緒後，他開始在紅綠燈十字路口奔跑，&ldquo;兌現&rdquo;承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://uf.cari.com.my/forumx/cforum/portal/201905/09/124322qffr7r99o5rd4i0r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuf.cari.com.my%2Fforumx%2Fcforum%2Fportal%2F201905%2F09%2F124322qffr7r99o5rd4i0r.png&h=f172e76c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民看到班雅的視頻後，調侃他應該在白天裡做這一件，才能讓人看見，&ldquo;你為什麼不在白天跑？&rdquo;，&ldquo;你應該在早上8點的時候跑......&ldquo;。除此以外，班雅的整體造型也遭到網友揶揄，認為他是時候去修一修頭髮了。"},{"pid":"66a43cb42a494c8ee4a0040734b5f26178dc5deb","tid":1146259,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"找數真漢子"},{"pid":"33283669185ccfd7084a224db0ac57d12e244f90","tid":1146259,"uid":132902,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:51:45.000Z","msg":"好過連登班走數撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a0d19d57435d2760e450fa2e87dbc9c41ef866","tid":1146259,"uid":144464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brDg61i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbrDg61i.jpg&h=3b2ca4d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾時到佢找"},{"pid":"fb05b0e6fa6a4dc8bc71a2f550eeeccfcba12438","tid":1146259,"uid":33730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"蛆狗出線 我針插龜頭牙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1058477/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1058477/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n相反呢啲走數狗真係賤種都不如"},{"pid":"25776c79502e5f4dc2bc4c60675da98a3b80585e","tid":1146259,"uid":174502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"個屎忽好正"}]}